cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.SE. 

The paper describes a platform for developing Semantic Web applications, which involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI) for building semantic data, as well as database technologies (cs.DB) for storing and retrieving that data. The platform also involves collaboration among developers (cs.SI) and the exploitation of semantic data (cs.IR). Finally, the paper discusses a practical case study on the design of a Web application (cs.SE) that uses the platform.
